# Additional Heritage-Specific Packages (Optional/Custom)
# These may need to be imported as custom packages or from Asset Store

# 3D Model Optimization
- Unity Cloud Build
- Unity Addressables for efficient asset loading
- LOD Group system for performance optimization

# Audio Enhancement
- Audio Mixer for spatial heritage audio
- 3D Spatial Audio for immersive soundscapes
- Timeline for synchronized audio-visual experiences

# Cultural Content Management
- Localization Package for multilingual support
- Custom Heritage Content Management System
- Cultural Asset Database Integration

# AR/VR Optimization
- AR Subsystems for cross-platform AR
- XR Interaction Toolkit for unified VR/AR interactions
- Platform-specific optimization packages

# Performance and Quality
- Universal Render Pipeline for optimized rendering
- Post Processing Stack for cinematic visuals
- Shader Graph for custom heritage materials
- Terrain Tools for landscape recreation

# Development and Testing
- Unity Test Framework
- Unity Profiler for performance optimization
- Memory Profiler for mobile optimization
- Device Simulator for testing various devices

# Heritage-Specific Integrations
- BHeri API Integration (Custom)
- MSME Training Module System (Custom)
- Cultural Content Validation Tools (Custom)
- Archaeological Data Import Tools (Custom)

# Build and Deployment
- Unity Cloud Build for automated builds
- Unity Analytics for user engagement tracking
- Unity Remote Config for A/B testing heritage content
- Platform-specific build optimization

# Version Control
- Unity Collaborate (alternative to Git LFS)
- Unity Version Control for large asset management
- Custom heritage asset versioning system

# Minimum Unity Version: 2022.3 LTS
# Recommended Unity Version: 2023.2 LTS
# Target API Levels:
# - Android: API 24 (7.0) minimum, API 33 (13.0) target
# - iOS: 12.0 minimum, 16.0 target
# - Windows: Windows 10 version 1903 minimum